Class DiaryItemOperationLog

java.lang.Object
DiaryItemOperationLog
public class DiaryItemOperationLog extends Object
DiaryItemOperationLog object is required for the undo functionality we are going to store in the stack the following objects: 1) added/updated/removed copy of a DiaryItem 2) DiaryItem Id 3) operation type: add, remove or update so, later when we call 'Undo' feature we can simply restore changed object
